.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, december, august, january, november
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, orange, corn, onion, pomegranate
5 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, mah-jongg, domino, go
The people have 5 different hobbies: photography, hiking, writing, drawing, woodworking
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes red
2. the person who's birthday is in swedish is the person who's hobby is writing
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating onion
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person eating orange
6. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's hobby is hiking
7. the person who likes yellow is the person playing canasta
8. the person eating corn is in the middle
9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left
10. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography
11. the person who's hobby is woodworkings is on the left or right of the person playing canasta
12. the person playing monopoly is the person eating cabbage
13. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing domino
14. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Birthday	|   january	|    december	|    june	|    august	|    swedish	|
| Hobby		|     photography	|    woodworking	|     hiking	|     drawing	|      writing	|
| Food	|    pomegranate	|     onion	|     corn	|    orange	|      cabbage	|
| Game		|   canasta	|    go	|  mah-jongg	|    domino	|   monopoly	|
